   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,783:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Important Notes 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,784:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: &
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,784:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Warnings
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,785:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  1 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,786:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Do NOT correct the 5 states with zero MRI sites.
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,788:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  This is a real signal of the ACR-only dataset
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,789:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: limitation. It will be acknowledged in the paper
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,789:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,790:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s Limitations section.
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,791:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,791:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Preserve leading zeros
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,792:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  in ZIP codes and FIPS codes. Always store them as strings, not numbers.
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,792:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,793:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: US territories are excluded.
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,793:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Only analyze 50 states + District of Columbia.
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,794:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  4 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,794:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,794:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,795:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Under Review
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,795:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,795:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  facilities (23 records) are included
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,796:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  in the primary analysis but excluded in a
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,797:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: sensitivity analysis.
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,797:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  5 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,797:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Nuclear Cardiology data
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,798:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  (separate sheet) is out of scope unless explicitly agreed upon with the
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,799:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: project lead.
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,799:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  6 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,799:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: County FIPS codes must be 5 digits.
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,800:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  State FIPS (2 digits) + County FIPS (3 digits) = 5-digit
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,801:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: combined code.
   DEBUG: 2026-05-22 16:29:59,802:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Document prepared: May 22, 2026
